![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578270290761-Z4ZQK6TJQTYUXPCPXROW/image-asset.jpeg)

Spider-Man: Far From Home comes out this week but let's not forget the first official outing of Tom Holland's Spider-Man in the teen comedy adventure Spider-Man: Homecoming. We are just 2 years removed from the 2nd Spider-Man reboot and the question is, does it hold up? How is Tom Holland as Spider-Man? What does the future of the web-slinger hold after the events of Avengers: Endgame? We talk all that and more in this retrospective episode that takes a deep dive into everything Spider-Man: Homecoming!   
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience, and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
